### Description

I'm having problems using views. I have not met anyone who may have been in the same situation, so I would like to know if there is any step that I am doing wrong. I just want to take the values ​​from the text fields and use them. However, they come in a format that would be semi-impossible to normalize.

### What type of issue is this? (place an `x` in one of the `[ ]`)
- [x] bug
