### Bug Report

Filling out the following details about bugs will help us solve your issue sooner.

#### Reproducible in:

slackclient version:2.5.0

python version:3.7

OS version(s):

#### Steps to reproduce:

1. POST any "view" content. JSON sent through slackclient library or JSON sent via API using requests

#### Expected result:

Normal values of text fields of views.
`'state': {
    'values': {
        'sub_block': {
            'txt_subject': {
                 'type': 'plain_text_input', 'value': 'This is the subject with special characters (ó á é í)'
}
     }
         }
             }`

#### Actual result:

`'state': {
    'values': {
        'sub_block': {
            'txt_subject': {
                 'type': 'plain_text_input', 'value': 'This+is+the+subject+with+special+characters+(u00e7u00e0u00e1u00f3)'
}
     }
         }
             }`

whitespaces are "+" instead of " "
unicode encode of special characters
linebreaks are "n" instead of "
"
